Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:02.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To visit someone named Daphne who \Nwas said to have met a dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:08.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we came to a traveler's inn named "Rise".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I had a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So of course, we fell right into the \Ntrap, and are completely shut in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:14.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing here, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a stomachache?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obviously not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san! Gray-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:20.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! Why are you attacking Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you are surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have no time to \Nstand there slack-jawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:36.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Fullbuster, finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:46.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wiping you out, is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Gray-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't he a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something similar happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something different \Nabout Gray this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something different?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this for real already, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:09.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He stripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu vs. Gray!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... You're seriously going for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes, that's the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a fake, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the honest to goodness \NGray Fullbuster, in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:49.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And just so you know, I'm not \Ncontrolling him using magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is doing this of his own free will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:04:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's punches could piss me off \Nthe same way as the real Gray's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:05.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tellin' me you {\i1}let{\i0} me \Npunch you as some sort of test?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:15.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Overdoing it, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain what's going on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A city without sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A city without sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Both of their powers are about equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:48.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Gray-san doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Fullbuster volunteered \Nto assist me of his own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of his own will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to Magnolia about 10 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to investigate the \Norigins of Natsu Dragneel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:12.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened upon Gray Fullbuster, who took \Ninterest in my story, and offered to assist me, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he's my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a complete traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can't believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that Gray and Daphne really do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...lllllike each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:27.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Juvia ain't gonna let this stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be a bloodbath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you are so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop butting into every conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the "city without sound" \Nthat Gray-san is talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you investigating Natsu-san exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold all questions for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have a snack, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spicy flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're being serious, then so will I!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:19.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the reason for this outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Natsu doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He should have returned by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He only went to ask about dragons, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely taking too long for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should calm down, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:42.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably just taking \Nhis time, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He had Wendy with him, so it's \Nstrange for him to be this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't like Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Draggin' a little girl around \Ntown all night ain't Manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:56.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried about the thing \Nthat suddenly attacked me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it also attacked Natsu and Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is worried about Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:06.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia feels unease in her heart, wondering \Nif something has happened to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think you're just worryin' too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He might've just gone straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:16.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The intuition of a woman \Nin love is never wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, sure! Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it so seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go search for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will come as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want you to stand by here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to leave \Nthe guild short-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful out there, Erza, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:15.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of their attacks can finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, they'll both use \Nup their energy and collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flaming Elbow of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes... He used the water from \Nthe pool and made a giant cage, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a decent head \Non your shoulders there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you now, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not some animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:24.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always planned on settling \Nthings with you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And today's the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your babbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who needs to shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:40.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on the first floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:42.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll need to stop the two \Nof them with my Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you use it in such a confined space, \Nyou might seriously injure everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go call for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes... Resistance is futile, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot escape from this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:10.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can beat her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is brightly colored \Nvegetable-flavored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Escaping isn't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this inn is an illusion I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An illusionary inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:31.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic, Concealment Magic, \Nhides people and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:35.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This inn was created with the \NConcealment Magic "Hidden Cage".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's a building \Nthat doesn't actually exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like your friends \Ncame to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san! Lucy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:57.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The inn Gray was talking about \Nshould have been around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sneak-attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling it would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you also attack Natsu and Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:55.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Maiden, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An impressive comedic reaction, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't said anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, save Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than one of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning to catch it off guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same ability as Virgo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has no grace in its hole digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you the proper way to dig a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your magic power \Nhas increased somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spica Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a powerful opponent, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself. Rest a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm countin' on you again. \NCan you handle it, Loke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the leader of the 12 Zodiacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pay back the favor you did me \Nby taking in Aries and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A different one, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:47.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say it's just a different \Nbody, but that doesn't seem the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:55.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to fight a spirit specializing \Nin fighting with brute power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In just one instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It raised its magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these things mimicking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san! Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like they \Ncan see us from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in league with \Nthose spiky-headed things?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes... Quite correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have various types of artificial \Nlife forms stored within this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Artificial life forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some type of golem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I made them with a system \Nwhere they automatically adapt
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to match the attributes of their opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that along \Nwith Natsu Dragneel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:46.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could gather information \Nabout a variety of wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you planning by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just have to stay tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:57.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The more data I gather, the \Nmore interesting it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:00.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're getting \Nto the end of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you're one majorly \Ntough bastard, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes... That's enough talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time, Gray Fullbuster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't called the Salamander for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:57.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that? I win, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:15:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad! I hit you somewhere I shouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kiddin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long are you gonna play...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet are freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Gray Fullbuster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:34.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You get high marks as my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:35.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Took a bit of work, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned on leading us here \Nfrom the start, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:49.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Plan worked like a charm, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so big when you \Njust lost the real fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw you in with 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please refrain from doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After finally capturing Salamander, \Ndon't mix in anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been dissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, my research will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy! Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon's egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:46.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ingeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon's egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A city without sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fun starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:33.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you have some trick \Nto match any ability I use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Adamantine Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And requip once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have the same ability, but no \None is faster at requipping than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The choice of weapons and armor is \Nsomething only experience can bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake will never be anything but a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:15.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the opponent mimics us, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did this before once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray for your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of Canis Minor, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is working perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure gave it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lift Concealment Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lacrima core, stand by for operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlock all joints!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neurotransmission lacrima \Nsensitivity, all green!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:48.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All impurities other than \NSalamander, get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, begin absorption of \NSalamander's magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:07.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonoid... activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb Salamander's magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:16.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are starting off quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the artificial dragon I invented!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it a Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking Salamander's magic power \Nand unveiling it for all to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:54.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:58.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray joined forces with this Daphne \Nperson and set a trap for Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:21:59.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray did?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not being controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it was of his own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really understand ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, what is this weird thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a Dragonoid, \Nand it's a man-made dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it's just a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd finally get to fight a dragon \Nwith my Dragon Slayer magic, but I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.20,0:24:10.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you're already captured inside it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.83,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Friendship \Nwill overcome the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:20.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm riding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:23.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Even though it's \Ntransportation? You're okay?
